Calculate the forecasts for a VAR out to a specified horizon Conditions on information at time "t"

forecast.Rd

Calculate the forecasts for a VAR out to a specified horizon Conditions on information at time "t"

Usage

forecast(var, horizon = 1)

Arguments

var

vars::VAR or svars object

horizon

number of steps out to calculate forecast

Value

forecast

Examples

x <- svars::USA
v <- vars::VAR(x, p = 2)
forecast(v, 10)
